# Shell working directory

The agent shell is already the project root. Run commands as-is; do not prefix with `cd` to this repo (no `cd c:\dev\vam-backstage && …` or similar).

`working_directory` on the run tool is for exceptional cases (subprojects, one-off paths); default is the repo root.

# Tools

Make sure to use proper tools when available rather than bare `ls` and such.
